            <description><![CDATA[前期工作
- Node.js 22 及以上版本。我使用的是`24.18.0LTS`版本
- 安装命令行`CLI`工具并进行换源。我使用的是`pnpm`淘宝源
- Markdown 语法编辑器
- Vs]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h1 id="从零开始安装vitepress" tabindex="-1">从零开始安装VitePress <a class="header-anchor" href="#从零开始安装vitepress" aria-label="Permalink to “从零开始安装VitePress”">&#8203;</a></h1>
<ArticleMetadata /><h2 id="前期工作" tabindex="-1">前期工作 <a class="header-anchor" href="#前期工作" aria-label="Permalink to “前期工作”">&#8203;</a></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/download" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Node.js</a> 22 及以上版本。我使用的是<code>24.18.0LTS</code>版本</li>
<li>安装命令行<code>CLI</code>工具并进行换源。我使用的是<code>pnpm</code>淘宝源</li>
<li>Markdown 语法编辑器</li>
<li>VsCode，Git</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="安装" tabindex="-1">安装 <a class="header-anchor" href="#安装" aria-label="Permalink to “安装”">&#8203;</a></h2>
<p><code>VitePress</code>可以单独使用，也可以安装到现有项目中。</p>
<p>在这两种情况下，都可以使用以下方式安装它：</p>
<table><tbody><tr><td>pnpm</td><td><div class="language-shell"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">shell</span><pre><!--::markdown-it-async::7dm09o3m3ql2kii48tgiop::--><code>pnpm add -D vitepress</code></pre>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>npm</td><td><div class="language-shell"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">shell</span><pre><!--::markdown-it-async::7tvcfk3e4q3zmah4p00ygd::--><code>npm i -D vitepress</code></pre>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>yarn</td><td><div class="language-shell"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">shell</span><pre><!--::markdown-it-async::gr75nsr9m7pcw91ykn77::--><code>yarn add -D vitepress</code></pre>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>bun</td><td><div class="language-shell"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">shell</span><pre><!--::markdown-it-async::8zdb9xwsm97nlpwhs11w5::--><code>bun add -D vitepress</code></pre>
</div></td></tr></tbody></table>
<details  class="details custom-block"><summary>如果你遇到了esbuild报错</summary>
<p>命令运行之后按<code>Enter</code></p>
<table><tbody><tr><td>pnpm</td><td><div class="language-shell"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">shell</span><pre><!--::markdown-it-async::ww1i8ijzsiskhfeakl0qu::--><code>pnpm approve-builds</code></pre>
</div></td></tr></tbody></table>
</details>
<h2 id="初始化向导" tabindex="-1">初始化向导 <a class="header-anchor" href="#初始化向导" aria-label="Permalink to “初始化向导”">&#8203;</a></h2>
<p><code>VitePress</code>附带一个命令行设置向导，可以帮助你构建一个基本项目。</p>
<table><tbody><tr><td>pnpm</td><td><div class="language-shell"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">shell</span><pre><!--::markdown-it-async::beb2sgpinyq5k06ysozia::--><code>pnpm vitepress init</code></pre>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>npm</td><td><div class="language-shell"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">shell</span><pre><!--::markdown-it-async::lkg8g67leom5oeqifwwb::--><code>npx vitepress init</code></pre>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>yarn</td><td><div class="language-shell"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">shell</span><pre><!--::markdown-it-async::5s5ub90fns6l6bxjqezc4r::--><code>yarn vitepress init</code></pre>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>bun</td><td><div class="language-shell"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">shell</span><pre><!--::markdown-it-async::xqplfus558yc67uxh7whd::--><code>bun vitepress init</code></pre>
</div></td></tr></tbody></table>
<table><tbody><tr><td>中文</td><td><div class="language-shell"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">shell</span><pre><!--::markdown-it-async::qco6mjczezlyot0rds7s::--><code>T  欢迎使用VitePress!
|
o  把你的文档设置在哪个目录?
|  ./docs
|
o  站点标题:
|  My Awesome Project
|
o  站点描述:
|  A VitePress Site
|
o  主题:
|  Default Theme
|
o  使用TypeScript支持?
|  Yes
|
o  在package.json中为npm添加VitePress命令?
|  Yes
|
—  结束! 现在你可以运行npm run docs:dev来启动它.</code></pre>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>官方原文</td><td><div class="language-shell"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">shell</span><pre><!--::markdown-it-async::laeq93omil6iijgjgajrk::--><code>T  Welcome to VitePress!
|
o  Where should VitePress initialize the config?
|  ./docs
|
o  Site title:
|  My Awesome Project
|
o  Site description:
|  A VitePress Site
|
o  Theme:
|  Default Theme
|
o  Use TypeScript for config and theme files?
|  Yes
|
o  Add VitePress npm scripts to package.json?
|  Yes
|
—  Done! Now run npm run docs:dev and start writing.</code></pre>
</div></td></tr></tbody></table>
<p>使用向导之后，应该运行一次<code>install</code>命令确保依赖正确安装</p>
<table><tbody><tr><td>pnpm</td><td><div class="language-shell"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">shell</span><pre><!--::markdown-it-async::98rglpijvxss4tczq8f1t8::--><code>pnpm install</code></pre>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>npm</td><td><div class="language-shell"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">shell</span><pre><!--::markdown-it-async::vob7wo96jihe2cz7ziwfa6::--><code>npm run install</code></pre>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>yarn</td><td><div class="language-shell"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">shell</span><pre><!--::markdown-it-async::zaa9b7nciob0nfmrwgoslc::--><code>yarn run install</code></pre>
</div></td></tr></tbody></table>
<p>这时你的文件结构如下</p>
<table><tbody><tr><td>explorer</td><td><div class="language-explorer"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">explorer</span><pre><!--::markdown-it-async::4ro8iim53ra4ad3on0wsdc::--><code>.
|- docs
|  |- .vitepress
|  |  |- config.mts
|  |  |- cache
|  |- api-examples.md
|  |- markdown-examples.md
|  |- index.md
|- package.json
|- pnpm-lock.yaml
|- pnpm-workspace.yaml</code></pre>
</div></td></tr></tbody></table>
<h2 id="快捷启动-非必须" tabindex="-1">快捷启动（非必须） <a class="header-anchor" href="#快捷启动-非必须" aria-label="Permalink to “快捷启动（非必须）”">&#8203;</a></h2>
<p>当前我们需要运行<code>pnpm docs:dev</code>来启动<code>VitePress</code>，这显然不友好。</p>
<p>通过修改<code>package.json</code>，我们可以简化这个操作</p>
<table><tbody><tr><td>package.json</td><td><div class="language-json"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">json</span><pre><!--::markdown-it-async::vtoruwabt28rste606ocv::--><code>{
  &quot;devDependencies&quot;: {
    &quot;vitepress&quot;: &quot;^1.6.4&quot;
  },
  &quot;scripts&quot;: {
    &quot;docs:dev&quot;: &quot;vitepress dev docs&quot;, // [!code --]
    &quot;docs:build&quot;: &quot;vitepress build docs&quot;, // [!code --]
    &quot;docs:preview&quot;: &quot;vitepress preview docs&quot; // [!code --]
    &quot;dev&quot;: &quot;vitepress dev docs&quot;, // [!code ++]
    &quot;build&quot;: &quot;vitepress build docs&quot;, // [!code ++]
    &quot;preview&quot;: &quot;vitepress preview docs&quot; // [!code ++]
  }
}</code></pre>
</div></td></tr></tbody></table>
<p>完成之后就可以通过<code>pnpm dev</code>来快速启动<code>VitePress</code>，命令运行之后按O快速打开网页</p>
<details  class="details custom-block"><summary>通过bat脚本快速启动（Linux使用sh脚本）</summary>
<p>将以下命令保存为脚本即可快速完成其功能</p>
<table><tbody><tr><td>dev.bat</td><td><div class="language-bat"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">bat</span><pre><!--::markdown-it-async::wzdm6nqqpgrcejh0iu6vhl::--><code>pnpm dev</code></pre>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>build.bat</td><td><div class="language-bat"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">bat</span><pre><!--::markdown-it-async::qxi35qtt38m9hkymnis7w::--><code>pnpm build</code></pre>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>preview.bat</td><td><div class="language-bat"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">bat</span><pre><!--::markdown-it-async::5ycl36v2q67adzpaswzj6k::--><code>pnpm preview</code></pre>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>install.bat</td><td><div class="language-bat"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">bat</span><pre><!--::markdown-it-async::uiqv7puc6p2oxiznhpw4c::--><code>pnpm install</code></pre>
</div></td></tr></tbody></table>
</details>
<h2 id="git忽略项" tabindex="-1">Git忽略项 <a class="header-anchor" href="#git忽略项" aria-label="Permalink to “Git忽略项”">&#8203;</a></h2>
<p>在<code>./</code>目录下创建<code>.gitignore</code>文件，添加以下内容，作用是在使用git上传时忽略这些文件</p>
<details  class="details custom-block"><summary>.gitignore的内容</summary>
<table><tbody><tr><td>.gitignore</td><td><div class="language-txt"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">txt</span><pre><!--::markdown-it-async::7b9x1ag2daxwode3jkh1dc::--><code># Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
lerna-debug.log*

# Diagnostic reports (https://nodejs.org/api/report.html)
report.[0-9]*.[0-9]*.[0-9]*.[0-9]*.json

# Runtime data
pids
*.pid
*.seed
*.pid.lock

# Directory for instrumented libs generated by jscoverage/JSCover
lib-cov

# Coverage directory used by tools like istanbul
coverage
*.lcov

# nyc test coverage
.nyc_output

# Grunt intermediate storage (https://gruntjs.com/creating-plugins#storing-task-files)
.grunt

# Bower dependency directory (https://bower.io/)
bower_components

# node-waf configuration
.lock-wscript

# Compiled binary addons (https://nodejs.org/api/addons.html)
build/Release

# Dependency directories
node_modules/
jspm_packages/

# Snowpack dependency directory (https://snowpack.dev/)
web_modules/

# TypeScript cache
*.tsbuildinfo

# Optional npm cache directory
.npm

# Optional eslint cache
.eslintcache

# Optional stylelint cache
.stylelintcache

# Optional REPL history
.node_repl_history

# Output of &#039;npm pack&#039;
*.tgz

# Yarn Integrity file
.yarn-integrity

# dotenv environment variable files
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# parcel-bundler cache (https://parceljs.org/)
.cache
.parcel-cache

# Next.js build output
.next
out

# Nuxt.js build / generate output
.nuxt
dist
.output

# Gatsby files
.cache/
# Comment in the public line in if your project uses Gatsby and not Next.js
# https://nextjs.org/blog/next-9-1#public-directory-support
# public

# vuepress build output
.vuepress/dist

# vuepress v2.x temp directory
.temp

# Sveltekit cache directory
.svelte-kit/

# vitepress build output
**/.vitepress/dist

# vitepress cache directory
**/.vitepress/cache

# Docusaurus cache and generated files
.docusaurus

# Serverless directories
.serverless/

# FuseBox cache
.fusebox/

# DynamoDB Local files
.dynamodb/

# Firebase cache directory
.firebase/

# TernJS port file
.tern-port

# Stores VSCode versions used for testing VSCode extensions
.vscode-test

# pnpm
.pnpm-store

# yarn v3
.pnp.*
.yarn/*
!.yarn/patches
!.yarn/plugins
!.yarn/releases
!.yarn/sdks
!.yarn/versions

# Vite files
vite.config.js.timestamp-*
vite.config.ts.timestamp-*
.vite/</code></pre>
</div></td></tr></tbody></table>
</details>
]]></content:encoded>
        </item>
